{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"9265a","heading":"Reports on certain licensing actions","label":"9265a Reports on certain licensing actions","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/ch99/schV/ptI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Otto Warmbier North Korea Nuclear Sanctions and Enforcement Act of 2019, and also as part of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2020, and not as part of the North Korea Sanctions and Policy Enhancement Act of 2016 which comprises this chapter.","Executive Documents","Delegation of FunctionsFunctions and authorities of President under this section delegated to Secretary of the Treasury and Secretary of Commerce by section 1(c) of Memorandum of President of the United States, , 85 F.R. 13717, set out as a note under .Feb. 21, 2020section 286yy of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Report required","label":"a Report required","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number and types of such licenses applied for during that period; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of such licenses issued during that period and information identifying the person receiving each such license.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Committees specified","label":"2 Committees specified","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Committee on Financial Services and the Committee on Foreign Affairs of the House of Representatives.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Committee on Banking, Housing, and Urban Affairs and the Committee on Foreign Relations of the Senate.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Submission of copies of licenses on request","label":"b Submission of copies of licenses on request","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary of the Treasury shall expeditiously provide a copy of any license identified in a report required by subsection (a)(1) to the Committee on Financial Services of the House of Representatives and the Committee on Banking, Housing, and Urban Affairs of the Senate if an appropriate Member of Congress requests a copy of that license not later than 30 days after submission of the report.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Form","label":"c Form","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Each report required by subsection (a), and each copy of a license submitted under subsection (b), shall be submitted in unclassified form but may include a classified annex.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Definitions","label":"d Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Appropriate Member of Congress","label":"1 Appropriate Member of Congress","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fd%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the chairman or ranking member of the Committee on Financial Services of the House of Representatives; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fd%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the chairman or ranking member of the Committee on Banking, Housing, and Urban Affairs of the Senate.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Covered regulatory provision","label":"2 Covered regulatory provision","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Part 743, 744, or 746 of title 15, Code of Federal Regulations.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Part 510 of title 31, Code of Federal Regulations.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s9265a/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs9265a%2Fd%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Any other provision of title 31, Code of Federal Regulations.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
